{"tid":1447972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警你老母」812 1300機場癱瘓","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:30.000Z","uid":66221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d7fd9874e55bbbcd8d8d7382b651cb329309ff","tid":1447972,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:19.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場"},{"pid":"130d6fdba42ccaefea917846c9c30835b6e69a3a","tid":1447972,"uid":268548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:23:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64c310564d8f5a02e61d834f9085b73bafe00893","tid":1447972,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"乜開post有限架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a149aa9008f4adc73740a9ad879e1ec697581b23","tid":1447972,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:18.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"1c37461aac96d0b312fcd31a487b7d162dd0415f","tid":1447972,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民抗爭 背水一戰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對港鐵不合作運動全民跳閘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.勇武轉入地下打狗<br />\n2.和理非要癱瘓機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為受傷被捕兄弟討回公道</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前線太多手足比捉 一定要升級癱瘓機場 全民打狗 選擇一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}